        "intro": "<p>We're sure you'll love your Proferlo furniture. If for any reason you're not completely satisfied, you can request a change-of-mind return within 14 days of receiving your order (conditions apply). We'll arrange a swap, replacement or refund. If an item has a fault, we can also arrange replacement parts, repairs or a replacement under warranty.</p>",
