    "faq_returns": {
      "type": "returns-warranty-faq",
      "blocks": {
        "q1": { "type": "faq", "settings": { "question": "When does the 14-day change-of-mind period start?", "answer": "<p>The 14-day change-of-mind period begins when your delivery is received. If a proof of delivery is not available, delivery is assumed to be one week from the dispatch date.</p>" } },
        "q2": { "type": "faq", "settings": { "question": "Will I be charged for return shipping on a change-of-mind return?", "answer": "<p>Within the 14-day change-of-mind period there is <strong>no restocking fee</strong> on items returned in their original condition and packaging — you simply cover the return shipping, and the initial delivery cost is also deducted from your refund where applicable. <strong>This also applies to free metro shipping products.</strong></p><p>For change-of-mind returns made during a Free Shipping Promotion, the cost of delivery both <em>to</em> and <em>from</em> you is deducted from your final refund. Our staff will quote this amount after you submit your returns request.</p>" } },
        "q3": { "type": "faq", "settings": { "question": "Which items are excluded from change-of-mind returns?", "answer": "<p>The following are excluded from change-of-mind returns:</p><ul><li>Items marked as <strong>“clearance”</strong> or discounted by more than 30% off RRP.</li><li>Any ex-display items purchased from our Showroom or Warehouse Clearance Sales.</li><li>Items with a <strong>“Made to Order”</strong> or <strong>“Special Order”</strong> lead time on their description.</li></ul>" } },
        "q4": { "type": "faq", "settings": { "question": "Do I need to keep the original packaging?", "answer": "<p>Yes. Original packaging is specially designed to protect the item in transit, so we recommend opening items carefully and keeping the packaging until you're certain you won't return them.</p><p>Any item not returned in its original packaging and/or original condition will incur a <strong>20% fee</strong>. It is your responsibility to ensure items are returned in the same condition they arrived in — Proferlo is not liable for damage that occurs during the return, whether by you or the courier. If you cannot supply the item in its original condition, a fee may apply or we may be unable to accept the return.</p>" } },
        "q5": { "type": "faq", "settings": { "question": "What condition do returned items need to be in, and when does the 20% fee apply?", "answer": "<p>We accept change-of-mind returns subject to the following terms:</p><ul><li>Within the 14-day change-of-mind period, items returned in their <strong>original condition and original packaging are not charged a restocking fee</strong> — you only cover the return shipping (the original delivery cost is also deducted where applicable).</li><li>A <strong>20% fee</strong> applies to returns made <strong>outside</strong> the change-of-mind period, or to items not returned in their original packaging or condition.</li><li>Items must be in <strong>new condition</strong> — we cannot accept items that have been scratched, stained, damaged, drilled into or otherwise altered. We reserve the right to refuse a refund where, in our reasonable assessment, the item has deteriorated due to wear and tear, misuse, or failure to take reasonable care.</li></ul><p><strong>Tip:</strong> take photographs of the item and its packaging before handing it to our delivery partners.</p>" } },
        "q6": { "type": "faq", "settings": { "question": "Can I return an item directly to your warehouse?", "answer": "<p>Yes. Items can be returned to our <strong>Acacia Ridge warehouse</strong>, and return shipping will not be charged if you do. Products must still pass through our returns request and be approved by our support staff before being returned.</p><p>Returning items to our warehouse without prior approval, or returning them to our showroom, will be denied.</p>" } },
        "q7": { "type": "faq", "settings": { "question": "How do I cancel or change my order?", "answer": "<p>If you wish to cancel your order before dispatch, or adjust the items in it, please contact our team. If an item has already left our warehouse, it will be considered under our change-of-mind return policy, including delivery costs.</p>" } }
      },
